snippet.title: Android Hunter A Steam Greenlight Trailer
snippet.description:
Android Hunter A is now on Steam Greenlight! Help get AHA greenlit by giving us a yes vote! 

http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=758895536&tscn=1473202852

The Android Hunter A Alpha Demo is now available to download for Windows 32-bit & Windows 64-bit! Head over to: http://androidhuntera.com/download/ to download the demo now!

Subscribe to our channel on YouTube to stay up to date on the latest
updates for Android Hunter A! 

https://www.youtube.com/user/DigiPIox

Visit all of our community pages! 

FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/androidhunteragame
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/digiplox
GOOGLE+: https://plus.google.com/+DigiploxNetCA/videos

Don't forget to like and follow us! 

http://androidhuntera.com/
